Saushs Koal appears to be staring rather intently at your mouth...
Use the stout rope on weakened sea creatures.
Deliver the captured sea creatures to Saushs Koal.
Finlessh one, finlessh one! How am I to glide through the watersh wishout watersh!? Or ssseek out that whish I crave? I cannot!
And what do I crave, you wonder? Teetsh! The teetsh of myriad beastshs!
Find for me feishty beastshs wish good teetshs, shmack them about until they're good and weak, and then bind them wish thish rope and bring them to me!
Let me shee, let me shink...a mnyiri, a morgawr, and a deep-shea leech. Bring me one of eacsh, alive─and mind the teetsh!
Remember: a mnyiri, a morgawr, and a deep-shea leech! Alive, if you would, and wish their lovely teetsh shtill intact!
Ahh, my finlessh friend! Have you my living loveliesh?
Shhhplendid! Shhhplendid! What big nashty teetsh you have! And now they are mine, mwahahaha! All mine!
Teetsh make for fine ssspearheadsh, and still finer gifts for female Ondo. The clutchmother and her attendants all delight in wearing sucsh jewelry.
But trutsh be told, I shimply adore teetsh of all shapsh and shizes. I am a collector wish an inshhhatiable need.
Why, the other day, I ashked another Ondo to give me his. Jusht a few! I even offered to pull them myshelf. But he grew so angry and refushed!
Shaaay... Your teetsh are rather nishe, finlessh one. Round and shhhiny and shmall. Would you be sho kind ash to favor me wish a few? The pulling will be quick and painlessh, I promish!
No? A shame. If you change your mind, come and find me. I shall be waiting. Always waiting, heh heh heh...
